
Very brief installation instructions are provided in README.

For details, see the Installation and Configuration tutorial

  http://www.circos.ca/tutorials/lessons/configuration/

################################################################

WINDOWS USERS

Please be attentive to the differences between UNIX and Windows, as
described in the above tutorial. 

Be aware that UNIX commands will not work on Windows.

If you are unfamiliar with the DOS command-line, refer to this tutorial

  http://www.bleepingcomputer.com/tutorials/tutorial76.html
